song.title: Quadrant (subtune 6) - My Endless Silkroad
song.info:
Original SID by Thomas Detert.
"(Once the song was 18 seconds, but now its a Silkroad) Some may like this remix, some may not. But why did I call it "My Endless Silkroad"? Inspiration came from the Silkroad.. If you don't know what I mean by this, then just contact me :)
My Greetings and respect goes to: Tassy, Larsec, Markus Schneider, Thomas Detert, Infamous, O2, Sidologie, Slaygon, Curlin, Kwed, Jihad and all in HiTMEN."
